gridboard.content:
<md-input-container style="margin:0;padding:0">
  <label>Filter by your country</label>
  <md-select ng-change="sendFilter('country',c)" ng-model="c">
    <md-option ng-value="inst.country " ng-repeat='inst in ds' >
    {{inst.country}}
    </md-option>
  </md-select>
</md-input-container>
